ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: How does the food app work?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Our food app allows you to browse restaurants, view menus, place orders, and track deliveries all in one convenient platform. Simply download the app, create an account, and start exploring delicious options in your area.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_2: Is there a minimum order amount?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Minimum order amounts may vary depending on the restaurant and your location. You can easily check the minimum order requirement for each restaurant within the app before placing your order.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: How can I track my order?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: Once you've placed an order, you can track its status in real-time through the app. You'll receive notifications about order confirmation, preparation, and when your food is out for delivery. You can also contact the driver or restaurant directly through the app if needed.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: Are there any special discounts or promotions?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: Yes! We regularly offer discounts, promotions, and special deals. Check the 'Offers' section in the app to see current promotions, and don't forget to enable push notifications to stay updated on the latest deals and exclusive offers.

FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Everything you need to know about our food app
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_1: How does the food ordering process work?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Simply browse restaurants, select your items, add them to your cart, and checkout. You can track your order in real-time and receive notifications about its status.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_2: What payment methods do you accept?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: We accept various payment methods including credit/debit cards, PayPal, and mobile wallets. Cash on delivery is also available for select locations.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: How long does delivery usually take?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: Delivery times vary depending on the restaurant and your location. On average, most orders are delivered within 30-45 minutes. You can see the estimated delivery time before placing your order.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: Can I customize my order or make special requests?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Yes! Many restaurants offer customization options for their menu items. You can also add special instructions or requests in the order notes during checkout.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: What if there's an issue with my order?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: If you experience any problems with your order, please contact our customer support team through the app or website. We're here to help and will work to resolve any issues promptly.
